affiliation: 3 Lawrence L. Schkade is Professor of Business Administration at North Texas State University. The author's recent research has been in the derivation of normative models of rational choice for individuals and the results have been published in a series of articles published in Annals of CPCU, Journal of Business, Journal of Risk and Insurance, and Revista de la Escuela de Contabilidad, and Economis y Administracion.
